==Annay s twallin==
iqqan-d f ufgan ad ur iẓaṛ atrms n tafukt s twallin-nns waḥdu-tnt, acku ɣik-ad iẓḍaṛ ad as-iddu iẓṛi-nns; g uzmz n utrms n tafukt, ar d-ttkkant tafukt tugt n wanawn n taḍḍangiwin [[Taliktṛamaɣniṭit|taliktṛamaɣniṭitin]]. Taḍḍangiwin ad gant taḍḍangiwin icqqan f iẓṛi n ufgan, zun d ukan :

#'''Iẓnẓaṛn n tafukt :''' Aẓnẓṛ n tafukt ur sgis ikṣuḍ ufgan walu f twallin ns, mac ig ur illi utrms afukan; acku g uzmz n utrms afukan ar d ttigutn iẓnẓaṛn n tafukt s wakal, ig ggutn iẓnẓaṛn ẓḍaṛn ad ssiḍnn tiwallin n ufgan.
#'''Iẓnẓaṛn ddu azggaɣ :''' Anaw-ad n iẓnẓaṛn ar ijddr aẓṭṭa n tiṭṭ n ufgan.
#'''Iẓnẓaṛn nnig (iggi) inibi :'''  Anaw ad n taḍḍangiwin talikṭṛamaɣniṭitin ihrc ula nttan f twallin n ufgan, acku ar isatti didas tugt n tazḍaṛt, mayad a f iẓḍaṛ a ijdr aẓṭṭa n twallin n ufgan.
