==Anawn n utrms n tafukt==
Atrms n tafukt ur igi yan yan, macc iga tugt n wanawn; nẓḍaṛ ad tn-nbḍu f [[Kkuẓ|kkuẓ]] n wanawn :
#'''Atrms amuttr''' : (s Tanglizt : total eclipse) ar ittili wanaw-ad akud nna d-iruḥ umalu n wayyur s wakal; g uzmz ad ar gis ttbayan taqqaṛiḍt n tafukt.
#'''Atrms buytli : ''' (s Tanglizt : annular eclipse) ar ittili akud-nna yaggug wayyur sg wakal, ur ar issnfay wayyur kullu tifawt n tafukt.
#'''Atrms abṛbuc : ''' (s Tanglizt : hybride eclipse) ar ittili wanaw ad akud-nna nẓṛa sin wanawn lli izwarn n utrms (amuttr d buytli) g kra n idɣarn g wakal iga gisn amuttr, g idɣaṛn yaḍnin iga gisn buytli. Nẓḍaṛ ad nini mas atrms abṛbuc iga tarkkust n sin wanawn imzwwra.
#'''Atrms angzam : ''' (s Tanglizt : partial eclipse) ar ittili akud-nna ur nẓḍar sg wakal ad niẓaṛ kullu taqqaṛiḍt n tafukt, acku amalu n wayyur ar nn-iṭṭaṛ g mani yaḍni (g kra n udɣar nn ibɛɛdn).

